# Binary assets must NEVER go through text/eol normalization — a CRLF
# conversion inside a GLB or audio file is silent corruption. (Discovered
# 2026-07-20: git's text heuristic misclassified some compressed GLBs and
# printed eol-conversion warnings on add.)
*.glb binary
*.gltf text
*.bin binary
*.png binary
*.webp binary
*.jpg binary
*.ico binary
*.ogg binary
*.mp3 binary
*.wav binary
*.ttf binary
*.sqlite binary
# Shell scripts run inside the Linux container — never CRLF.
*.sh text eol=lf
